## Title: Super Swing Timer
## Notes: Melee and ranged swing timer for Classic and TBC. Includes Blizzard options panel support, class-colored swing bars, in-addon texture previews, a latency-aware hunter Auto Shot cooldown line, a dedicated ranged texture picker, a UnitAura-aware paladin seal breakpoint line, and color-coded shaman weave assist overlays with per-family toggles that stay above the bar fill.
